title: Dakine Vault Pack 25L
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Vault Pack 25L in Black.
Vault Pack 25L Features: 
- Padded laptop sleeve
- Fits most 17" laptops
- Front pocket fits iPad
- Deployable water bottle pocket
- Breathable Dri Mesh back panel
- Fleece lined phone pocket
- Load compression straps
- Adjustable sternum strap
